@startuml
actor Buyer
actor Admin

Buyer --> (Client Application): Request Data
(Client Application) --> (Access Control Subsystem): Verify Access
(Access Control Subsystem) --> (Data Storage Subsystem): Access Data
(Data Storage Subsystem) --> (Client Application): Provide Data
(Client Application) --> Buyer: Display Data

Admin --> (Admin Application): Manage Data
(Admin Application) --> (Access Control Subsystem): Verify Access
(Access Control Subsystem) --> (Data Storage Subsystem): Access Data
(Data Storage Subsystem) --> (Admin Application): Provide Data
(Admin Application) --> Admin: Display Data

(Client Application) --> (Logging Subsystem): Log Event
(Admin Application) --> (Logging Subsystem): Log Event
@enduml
